    "title": {
      "rendered": "5 Types of Online Campaigns Ideal for the New .NGO Domains"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h6><a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19546\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-19546\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"5 Types of online campaigns ideal for the new .NGO domains facebook\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/5-Types-of-online-campaigns-ideal-for-the-new-.NGO-domains-facebook.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Written by\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a> who works as an Ambassador for the Public Interest Registry &#8211; the nonprofit operator of the <a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">.ORG, .NGO and .ONG domains</a>.</h6>\n<p>The fact that the .NGO domains listed below (except <strong><a href=\"http://techreport.ngo/\" target=\"_blank\">techreport.ngo</a></strong>) and in the graphic to the right are still available is astounding and for early adopters with vision, an opportunity to <strong><a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">register a domain for good</a></strong> not seen since the domain registration craze of the late 1990&#8217;s. While most .ORG domains were taken years ago, the new .NGO domain is still <em>relatively</em> available and they make excellent microsites and redirects for online fundraising, cause awareness, and advocacy campaigns \u2013 and not just because you&#8217;re likely to still be able to register your first or second choice, but also because the new .NGO domain requires proof of legal status to register and use for web and email communications. The legal validation requirement lends instant credibility to your nonprofit&#8217;s\u00a0online brand and as use of the domain spreads around the globe, online donors and supporters will soon come to understand that when they see an online campaign hosted on a .NGO domain, it is an online campaign that can be trusted and donated to without hesitation.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1) Fundraising Campaigns<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">givewater.ngo</a> \u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldWaterDay\" target=\"_blank\">#WorldWaterDay</a><a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19559\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-19559\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/givewater.png?resize=600%2C414\" alt=\"givewater\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/givewater.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/givewater.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h2>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19570 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=500%2C20\" alt=\"white bar\" width=\"500\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=300%2C12&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2) Cause Awareness Campaigns<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">worldelephantday.ngo</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldElephantDay\" target=\"_blank\">#WorldElephantDay</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19562\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-19562\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/worldelephantday.png?resize=600%2C414\" alt=\"worldelephantday\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/worldelephantday.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/worldelephantday.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19570 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=500%2C20\" alt=\"white bar\" width=\"500\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=300%2C12&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3) Online Pledge\u00a0Websites<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">adoptdontshop.ngo</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/adoptdontshop\" target=\"_blank\">#adoptdontshop</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19566\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-19566\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/adoptdontshop.png?resize=600%2C414\" alt=\"adoptdontshop\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/adoptdontshop.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/adoptdontshop.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19570 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=500%2C20\" alt=\"white bar\" width=\"500\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=300%2C12&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4) Online Petition\u00a0Campaigns<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">nationalparks.ngo</a> \u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/savenationalparks\" target=\"_blank\">#SaveNationalParks</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/nationalparks.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19567\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-19567\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/nationalparks.png?resize=600%2C414\" alt=\"nationalparks\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/nationalparks.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/nationalparks.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19570 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=500%2C20\" alt=\"white bar\" width=\"500\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/white-bar.jpg?resize=300%2C12&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5) A Report Launch Website<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">techreport.ngo</a>\u00a0\u2605 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ngotech16\" target=\"_blank\">#NGOTECH16</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/techreport.ngo_.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19568\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-19568\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/techreport.ngo_.png?resize=600%2C314\" alt=\"techreport.ngo\" width=\"600\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/techreport.ngo_.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/techreport.ngo_.png?resize=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 class=\"proximanovabold largerfont nomargin largesttopmargin lineheight32 colordarkgray\">Is your first choice of the new .NGO and .ONG domains still available? <em>Likely, but not for long.</em> Search <a href=\"https://www.name.com/domains/tech4good\" target=\"_blank\">name.com and\u00a0use code <span class=\"customred\"><strong>TECH4GOOD</strong></span></a>\u00a0through April 30 to <span class=\"customred\"><strong>save 50%</strong></span> and register your .NGO for only $20US.</h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><em><strong>Please Note:</strong> </em></span>The NGO acronym translates to \u201cONG\u201d in regions where Spanish, French, Italian, and Portuguese are spoken. When your nonprofit registers .NGO, <em>you\u2019ll automatically receive a complimentary .ONG domain</em> as well.</h2>\n",
